snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 16 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 16th February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra

Haris Waheed

snippet.title: No More Lies | Election 2023  | Dreamz Unlimited | CEO Nagaland
snippet.description:
Why should you vote?
India is the largest democracy in the world. The right to vote and more
importantly the exercise of franchise by the eligible citizens is at the heart of
every democracy. We, the people, through this exercise of our right to vote
have the ultimate power to shape the destiny of country by electing our
representatives who run the Government and take decisions for the growth,
development and benefit of all the citizens.

This video is produced by 
Chief Electoral Officer (CEO), Kohima, Nagaland

Download the cVigil App here;
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=in.nic.eci.cvigil&hl=en_IN&gl=US

snippet.title: Sasta Biig Bosss 2 | Parody | Ashish Chanchlani
snippet.description:
Acv presents the second season of “SASTA BIIG BOSSS”
Chalo pehle brand waalo ka description daalte because PAISAAAA 

WOW Skin Science: ACV Shampoo & Face Wash

Amazon: https://amzn.to/3Xs8zo1 
Flipkart: https://bit.ly/3K06s7I
Nykaa: http://bit.ly/3HVUQ2W

BuyWow: http://bit.ly/3XnDn9y
(Use ASHISHWOW20 for an extra 20% discount)

Haan haan maalum
Hai hume bahut late ho gaya aane mein
Pure 10 nahi nahi 11 mahine lag gaye hume
Lekin tum log ko kya batau aisi fatti padi thi hum log ka kuch aisa project tha jisse plan karte karte karte 6-7 mahine aise nikle hume pata hi nai chala
Fir humne ye saal ka bigg boss dekha aur decide kiya abhi toh hum season 2 banaenge hi kaise bhi
Wo jo project hai jiski baat kar raha hu abhi back burner pe hai but promise hai hum usse kaise bhi aapke saamne laaenge😍

Abhi subah ke 6 baje main ye description bathroom mein likh raha hu seth log toh please deri ke lie maaf kar do baaki tum log hi seth ho mere dhani ho muje maalum hai naraazgi hogi lekin utna hi pyaar bhi karte ho
Chalo abhi video ka Favourite part comment karo aur apna fav dialogue bhi likh lo

Chalo abhi production ka batao is video ka

Actors : wahi sasti team jisme dusre actors ki kami hoti, Akash Dodeja aka jadoo aka gareeb Kunal Chhabhria aka is baar wo kisi ke baap nahi gaya Vibhu Varshney humare video ke super star Simran Dhanwani rotlu pitbul Rohit Sadhwani belt waala anti-singham Tanish Sirwani sandaswala Grishim Nawani dubai waala Akash Jagtap thapad khaane waala Paras rupani playground ka rejected player, Ritesh Sadhwani bhi tha video mein bas ek scene mein kyunki saala gumm ho gaya tha Shivkumar Parthasarathy as humare big-bull Vivek Menon humare super super star as humare host
And ajay bhai jinhone teddy bear ka body double play kiya 

Writer & Director : main hi hu saalo
Editor : wo bhi main hi hu saalo
Background music - Vivek-Abhishek (inka channel dekho bahut talented hai mere bhai log : https://youtube.com/c/VIVEKABHISHEK)
Production Head: Jashan Sirwani & Tanish Sirwani (saara paisa ye log khaa jaate rent aur camera ka😡)
DOP : Ujjawal Gayakwad,Sidharth Kedare
Assistant DOP : Hemendra Singh, Yogi
Gaffer : Ramchandra Vishwakarma
Sound : Satya Narayan
Lights : Golden Lights 
Location : Mania Location
Art : Ravi Kondke and Team
Makeup : Akbar Ali Shaikh and Team
Production : Tushar Manejar and Team

#SastaBiigBosss2 #AshishChanchlani #Acv

snippet.title: மகா சிவராத்திரி 2023 விரத முறை, வழிபடும் முக்கிய நேரம், பலன்கள் | Maha Sivarathri Fasting & Worship
snippet.description:
சிவபுராணம் தினமும் கேட்பதற்காக தமிழ் & ஆங்கில வரிகளுடன் | Sivapuranam in my voice with lyrics
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MiRay98qWCY

மஹா மிருத்யுஞ்ஜய மந்திரம் (108 முறை எனது குரலில்) | Maha Mrityunjaya Mantra (108 times chanting)
https://youtu.be/l3d7wqYb0DY


சிவராத்திரி விரதம் இருக்கும் முறை, செய்ய வேண்டிய 4 கால பூஜைகள், அபிஷேகங்கள், அர்ச்சனைகள், நெய்வேத்தியம், படிக்க வேண்டிய பதிகங்கள், பூஜை செய்ய வேண்டிய நேரம் என அனைத்து தகவல்களையும் திருமதி. தேச மங்கையர்க்கரசி அம்மா அவர்கள் இந்த வீடியோவில் விளக்கமாக பதிவிட்டுள்ளார். 

சிவராத்திரி விரதம் மேற்கொள்ளும் உங்கள் நண்பர்கள் மற்றும் உறவினர்களுக்கு இந்த வீடியோவை ஷேர் செய்து அவர்களும் அறியும்படி செய்யுங்கள்.  

- ஆத்ம ஞான மையம்

snippet.title: Paranormal Activities को Track करते-करते गई किसकी जान? | CID | Nostalgia | सीआईडी | 15 Feb 2023
snippet.description:
Paranormalist Aliya gets killed in the haveli where a hotel was supposed to get constructed. Team C.I.D. investigates the case and also questions Aliya's group who were keeping an eye on Aliya's movements in the camera. Dr. Salunkhe reveals to Team C.I.D. about a sudden heart attack. Did Aliya die due to a sudden heart attack? Stay tuned to find out!

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode No: 1104
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh
 
#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #CID Nostalgia #LIVCrime #NewCID #LatestCID #Crime

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch all the episodes of the CID Nostalgia :
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIVJzesdfwktpj4U8HRY8p6k

snippet.description:
Manchester City are top of the Premier League after a 3-1 victory over Arsenal in north London.

Jack Grealish and Erling Haaland scored the second-half goals that proved the difference in an entertaining top-of-the-table clash.

Kevin De Bruyne’s opportunistic finish midway through the first half had opened the scoring before Arsenal levelled through a controversial penalty shortly before the break.

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 17 Teaser - 16th February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 17 Teaser - 16th February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas

Haris Waheed

snippet.title: The Prema Bua Show | 2 Foreigners In Bollywood
snippet.description:
Download Probo & Earn Money:- https://probo-in.onelink.me/1kre/2ForeignersInBollywoodFeb

Prema Bua is a 77 year old lady from a small village in Madhya Pradesh. At this later stage in life she has decided to explore new things and see what the world has to offer. In this episode she decides to travel to Mumbai and we find her in a 5-star hotel. She’s excited to try some fancy continental food but to her big surprise the dishes are quite familiar and let’s just say that her expectations are not met…

#2foreignersinbollywood #2fib #ad

snippet.title: 45 मिनिटांत महाशिवरात्री उपवास थाळी | फ्रेंच फ्राइज, गोड पुऱ्या, साबुदाणा खिचडी Mahashivratri Thali
snippet.description:
*सरिताज किचनची शुद्ध, पारंपरिक आणि केमिकल विरहित लाकडी घाण्याची तेलं ऑर्डर करण्यासाठी ८९५६१६८७८२ या नंबर वर व्हॉटस अॅप मेसेज किंवा कॉल करा. 
 किंवा खालील लिंक वर क्लिक करून ऑर्डर बूकिंग करा 
 https://saritaskitchenofficial.com/

To Order Sarita’s Kitchen Chemical Free Pure Cold Pressed Oils Whats App OR Call on 8956168782
Or Click on the link below to book the order – 
https://saritaskitchenofficial.com/

Mahashivratri Upvas Thali / महाशिवरात्री उपवास थाळी

1. रताळ्याच्या घाऱ्या / उपवासाच्या पुऱ्या  
2. साबुदाणा खिचडी 
3. ओल्या नारळाची खीर, 
4. बटाटा fries    
उपवाससाठी रताळ्याचे घारगे | Sweet potato Puri for Fasting  – 
साहित्य | Ingredients 
• रताळे 250 ग्राम्स | Sweet Potato 250 grams 
• किसलेला गूळ ½ कप | Chopped Jaggery ½ Cup
• मीठ चवीनुसार | Salt to taste
• वरई पीठ 1 ते सवा कप अंदाजे | Sama Flour 1-1 ¼ Cup Approx
• तळण्यासाठी तेल | Oil for frying
Method – 
• Wash sweet potatoes well, keep it in a pressure cooker tin, put some water at the bottom of the pressure cooker, put sweet potato tin into the pressure cooker, and take 2 whistles. 
• Let the pressure release from pressure cooker, take potato out and let it cool down completely. 
• Once cool down, peel the skin from potato and grate the potato.
• Add grated jaggery and salt to taste and mix well.
• Then add sama flour to make semi soft dough, cover the dough and let it rest for 10 mintues,
• After mins, take small lemon sized ball from the dough.
• On rolling pad put butter paper, apply some ghee onto it , put ball onto it again put butter paper on the top of the dough and gently press the dough with the help of a plate. 
• Puri is ready, deep fry puri on med to high heat. 

Sabudana Khichadi Recipe | साबुदाणा खिचडी रेसिपी 
• साबूदाणा 1 कप | Sago 1 Cup 
• साजूक तूप 3 चमचे | Ghee 2-3 tbsp
• बटाटा 1 मध्यम | Potato 1 med
• हिरव्या मिरची तुकडे 1 tbsp | Green chillies chopped 1 tbsp
• साखर 1 चमचा | Sugar 1 tsp
• सैंधव मीठ चवीनुसार | Pink Himalayan Salt to taste
• भाजलेल्या दाण्याचा जाडसर कूट 3/4 कप | Raosted peanuts crushed ¾ cup
• दूध 2-3 tbsp | Milk 2-3 tbsp
Method –
• Wash the sago well, keep some water into it and soak it overnight or for about 5-6 hours. (you add some milk while soaking the sago) 
• Heat up some oil / ghee into a kadhai add green chilies and potatoes and some salt and saute on med heat till potatoes get nice golden brown color 
• Then add sugar, roasted peanut crushed and saute for a min on low heat.
• Then add soaked sago and salt to taste and saute on med heat for about 3-4 minutes, then cover and cook on low heat for 2 minutes.
• After 2 minutes add milk and again stir for abut 2 minutes and again cover and cook for a min on low heat. 
• After a min check again, stir for a min and serve hot. 

 नारळाची खीर रेसिपी | Coconut Kheer Recipe 
• ओल्या नारळाचा चव 1 कप | Fresh coconut scraped 1 Cup
• दूध अर्धा लिटर | Milk ½ Liter 
• साखर ½ कप | Sugar ½ Cup
• काजू , बदाम पिस्ता काप | Cashew, Almond pista 
• साजूक तूप 1 चमचा | Ghee 1 tsp
Method –
• Heat some ghee into a kadhai and add scraped coconut and roast for 2-3 mins.
• Then add sugar and some water and mix well and cover and cook for 2 mins on low heat.
• Then add billed milk, kesar and dryfruits chopped and cook on low heat for 5-6 mins.
• At the last add cardamom pw and turn off the heat. 

उपवासाचे फिंगर चिप्स | बटाटा फ्राइज रेसिपी | Potato Fries Recipe
• मोठे लांब बटाटे 2-3 | Potatoes 2-3
• सैंधव मीठ चवीनुसार | Pink Himalayan Salt to taste
• वरई पीठ ¼ कप (गरजेप्रमाणे) | Sama Flour ¼ Cup 
• मिरची पावडर 1/2 tsp | Red Chilly pw ½ tsp
• तळण्यासाठी तेल | Oil for frying 
Method –
• Wash and peel the potato skin, and chop like finger chips.
• Wash chopped potatoes for 3-4 times and strain well
• Boil some water into a pan, once water is boiling add pink Himalayan salt and potatoe pices.
• Boil potatoes for 2-3 mins on high heat, take the potatoes out and drain extra water.
• Spread potatoes onto a cotton cloth and wipe gently to remove excess water. And keep it into deep freezer for 15 minutes.
• Then into a bowl add samal flour, salt and red chilly pw and add water to make thick slurry. 
• Deep potatoes into the ready slurry and deep fry into hot oil. 
#mahashivratrithali #upvasachithali #upvasthalirecipe #sabidanakhichadi #bananachips #potatofriesrecipe #specialfastingthali #thali #vegthali #saritaskitchenthali #thalirecipe #saritaskitchenthalirecipe #ekadashispecialthali #upvasachithali #महाशिवरात्रीथाळी #उपवासचीथाळी #उपवासाचेघारगे #साबूदाणाखिचडी

• मोठे लांब बटाटे 2-3 | Potatoes 2-3
• सैंधव मीठ चवीनुसार | Pink Himalayan Salt to taste
• वरई पीठ ¼ कप (गरजेप्रमाणे) | Sama Flour ¼ Cup 
• मिरची पावडर 1/2 tsp | Red Chilly pw ½ tsp
• तळण्यासाठी तेल | Oil for frying 
Method –
• Wash and peel the potato skin, and chop like finger chips.
• Wash chopped potatoes for 3-4 times and strain well
• Boil some water into a pan, once water is boiling add pink Himalayan salt and potatoe pices.
• Boil potatoes for 2-3 mins on high heat, take the potatoes out and drain extra water.
• Spread potatoes onto a cotton cloth and wipe gently to remove excess water. And keep it into deep freezer for 15 minutes.
• Then into a bowl add samal flour, salt and red chilly pw and add water to make thick slurry. 
• Deep potatoes into the ready slurry and deep fry into hot oil.

Ingredients:
Kavathachi Chutney
• 2 Kavath / Wood apple
• 1 cup Gudh
• 1 tsp Red chili powder
• 1/2 tsp Black salt
• Salt to taste
Sabudana Khichadi
• 1 cup Sabudana
• 1 tsp Ghee
• 1/2 tsp Cumin seed
• 2~3 chopped Green chilies
• 1 boiled, peeled and chopped Potato
• 1/2 cup roasted Peanut powder
• Salt to taste
• Sugar to taste (Optional)
Ratalyacha Kis
• 3~4 Ratali / Sweet potato
• 1 tbsp Ghee
• 1/2 tsp Cumin seeds
• 2 chopped Green chilies
• Salt to taste
• 1 tsp roasted Peanut powder
Shengdanyachi Amti
• 2 Green chilies
• 1/2 cup roasted Peanut powder
• Water
• 1 tbsp Ghee
• 1/2 tsp Cumin seeds
• 1 Cinnamon stick
• 2 green Cardamom
• 3~4 Cloves
• 3~4 Black peppercorns
• Water to adjust the consistency
• Salt to taste
• 1 tbsp Tamarind-Gudh pulp

Method:
Kavathachi Chutney
• Break open the kavath and take out the pulp. 
• Add gudh and mash it well together. 
• The quantity of the pulp and gudh must be same means for 1 cup pulp use 1 cup gudh. 
• Add red chili powder, black salt, salt and mix it well together. Kavathachi chutney is all ready.
Sabudana Khichadi
• Wash sabudana really good 3-4 times and soak it in enough water overnight or at least 4-5 
  hours. 
• Heat up ghee in a pan and add cumin seeds. 
• When cumin seeds splutter add green chilies and fry for few seconds. 
• Add potato, soaked sabudana, roasted peanut powder, salt, sugar and mix well. 
• Adding sugar is optional. You can skip it if you don’t want. 
• Fry khichadi well together. 
• Cover and steam on low heat for about 5-7 minutes. Sabudana khichadi is all ready.
Ratalyacha Kis
• Wash the ratali well and peel them. 
• Grate it into long shreds. 
• Heat up ghee in a pan and add cumin seeds. 
• When cumin seeds splutter add green chilies and fry well. 
• Add grated ratali and fry well. 
• Cover and steam for about 4-5 minutes. 
• Add salt, roasted peanut powder and mix well. Ratalyacha kis is all ready. 
Shengdanyachi Amti
• Blend green chilies, roasted peanut powder together well once. 
• You can use 1/4 cup fresh coconut and 1/4 cup roasted peanut powder if you want. 
• Add water and blend it into paste. 
• Heat up ghee in a pan and add cumin seeds, cinnamon, cardamom, cloves, black 
  peppercorns. 
• Fry for few seconds. Add the blended paste, water to adjust the consistency, salt, tamarind-
  gudh pulp. 
• Mix well and simmer amti for about 5-6 minutes. Shengdanyachi amti is all ready.

मधुराज रेसिपीचं पुस्तक खरेदी करण्यासाठी खालील लिंकवर क्लिक करा.

Combo Pack of all 4 Maduras Masala - https://amz.run/4WSK
किंवा ९१३६८२२२२४ या नंबर वर व्हॉटसऍप मेसेज करा

Ingredients:
Kavathachi Chutney
• 2 Kavath / Wood apple
• 1 cup Gudh
• 1 tsp Red chili powder
• 1/2 tsp Black salt
• Salt to taste
Sabudana Khichadi
• 1 cup Sabudana
• 1 tsp Ghee
• 1/2 tsp Cumin seed
• 2~3 chopped Green chilies
• 1 boiled, peeled and chopped Potato
• 1/2 cup roasted Peanut powder
• Salt to taste
• Sugar to taste (Optional)
Ratalyacha Kis
• 3~4 Ratali / Sweet potato
• 1 tbsp Ghee
• 1/2 tsp Cumin seeds
• 2 chopped Green chilies
• Salt to taste
• 1 tsp roasted Peanut powder
Shengdanyachi Amti
• 2 Green chilies
• 1/2 cup roasted Peanut powder
• Water
• 1 tbsp Ghee
• 1/2 tsp Cumin seeds
• 1 Cinnamon stick
• 2 green Cardamom
• 3~4 Cloves
• 3~4 Black peppercorns
• Water to adjust the consistency
• Salt to taste
• 1 tbsp Tamarind-Gudh pulp

Method:
Kavathachi Chutney
• Break open the kavath and take out the pulp. 
• Add gudh and mash it well together. 
• The quantity of the pulp and gudh must be same means for 1 cup pulp use 1 cup gudh. 
• Add red chili powder, black salt, salt and mix it well together. Kavathachi chutney is all ready.
Sabudana Khichadi
• Wash sabudana really good 3-4 times and soak it in enough water overnight or at least 4-5 
  hours. 
• Heat up ghee in a pan and add cumin seeds. 
• When cumin seeds splutter add green chilies and fry for few seconds. 
• Add potato, soaked sabudana, roasted peanut powder, salt, sugar and mix well. 
• Adding sugar is optional. You can skip it if you don’t want. 
• Fry khichadi well together. 
• Cover and steam on low heat for about 5-7 minutes. Sabudana khichadi is all ready.
Ratalyacha Kis
• Wash the ratali well and peel them. 
• Grate it into long shreds. 
• Heat up ghee in a pan and add cumin seeds. 
• When cumin seeds splutter add green chilies and fry well. 
• Add grated ratali and fry well. 
• Cover and steam for about 4-5 minutes. 
• Add salt, roasted peanut powder and mix well. Ratalyacha kis is all ready. 
Shengdanyachi Amti
• Blend green chilies, roasted peanut powder together well once. 
• You can use 1/4 cup fresh coconut and 1/4 cup roasted peanut powder if you want. 
• Add water and blend it into paste. 
• Heat up ghee in a pan and add cumin seeds, cinnamon, cardamom, cloves, black 
  peppercorns. 
• Fry for few seconds. Add the blended paste, water to adjust the consistency, salt, tamarind-
  gudh pulp. 
• Mix well and simmer amti for about 5-6 minutes. Shengdanyachi amti is all ready.

snippet.description:
What if love was only a text away?💕📱 #LoveAgainMovie, featuring new music by @CelineDion, starring @priyankachopra and Sam Heughan is exclusively in movie theaters Mother’s Day. 

Text “LOVE” to (310) 634-1918 for exclusive content from Love Again. 📱

Visit our site: 
https://www.LoveAgain.movie

Follow Us on Social:
https://www.facebook.com/LoveAgainMovie
https://www.instagram.com/LoveAgainMovie
https://www.twitter.com/LoveAgainMovie

Subscribe to the Sony Pictures YouTube Channel for more exclusive content: 
http://bit.ly/SonyPicsSubscribe

What if a random text message led to the love of your life? In this romantic comedy, dealing with the loss of her fiancé, Mira Ray sends a series of romantic texts to his old cell phone number… not realizing the number was reassigned to Rob Burns’ new work phone. A journalist, Rob is captivated by the honesty in the beautifully confessional texts. When he’s assigned to write a profile of megastar Celine Dion (playing herself in her first film role), he enlists her help in figuring out how to meet Mira in person…and win her heart. Starring Priyanka Chopra Jonas, Sam Heughan and Celine Dion and featuring multiple new songs from Dion, Love Again, written for the screen and directed by Jim Strouse, is only in theaters May 12, 2023.

                 Judwa behene Divya aur Drishti ko apne janam se mila hai shakti ka vardaan. Drishti bhavishya kaal ko dekh sakti hai aur Divya ussey badal sakti hai. snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3695 - 15 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3695: Bhoot Ka Hungama
--------------------------------------------------------
The Purush Mandali members with Goli and Gogi explore the terrace for the ghost while the members of the Gokhuldham society continue to be afraid of the enigmatic figure. As they believed Iyer to be the ghost, Champaklal and Jetha with the Mahila Mandal beat him up. The Purush Mandali becomes alarmed when they cannot locate Iyer among them, believing that the ghost must have abducted him. The Gokuldham members discover a speaker in the center of the compound, which increases their terror. Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3695, 15 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000209565

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3696 - 16 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3696: Prankster Ki Shart
--------------------------------------------------------
The Gokuldham residents are yet to discover the nuisance maker, and out of fear, they wander inside the clubhouse. Suddenly, Sodhi yells that he has found the mystery man, but after turning on the lights, it turns out to be Popatlal. Later, they heard someone speaking over loudspeakers. It turns out to be the mystery man who has been using these speakers to talk to everyone. He tells Gokuldham residents that he will reveal his identity if they agree to his condition. What could be his demand to the Gokuldham dwellers? Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Shraddha ने लिया Thapki का भेष | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 624
snippet.description:
Shraddha ने लिया Thapki का भेष | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 624

For Bani's safety, the Pandeys decide to leave her at Amma Mai's residence and come back later with a better plan. After the family leaves, Thapki makes an agreement with Amma Mai, asking her to take Bani as her daughter-in-law. But little does anyone know that it's Shraddha in disguise. Will Thapki find out about this before it's too late?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: Pineapple Kesari Recipe in Tamil | How to make Pineapple Rava Kesari at home
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make pineapple kesari recipe in tamil. In this video we are going to use chunks of pineapple to make a flavorful kesari recipe at home. The pineapple flavor works very well with the taste profile of rava / sooji. This cooking method results in well cooked kesari with well separated grains of sooji rava. 
#kesarirecipe #pineapplekesari 

Friends, please do try this pineapple rava kesari recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

Ingredients:
1 cup Pineapple 
1 cup Rava
1.25 cup Sugar
1/2 cup Ghee(8 tbsp)
1/3 cup Oil(6 tbsp)
pinch of Salt
Yellow food color
10 Cashews
2-3 tbsp Raisins
1/4 tsp Cardamom powder

आर्थिक संकट से झुंझ रहे पाकिस्तान को अब उनकी जनता का भी साथ नहीं मिल रहा. पाकिस्तान के एक युवक का कहना है कि कुछ लोगों को इंग्लैंड जाना चाहते है, LSA जाना चाहते है. लेकिन मैं लखनऊ जाना चाहता हूँ, क्योंकि हम वहीं से है. 

Pakistan, which is grappling with the economic crisis, is no longer getting the support of its people. A young man from Pakistan says that some people want to go to England, want to go to LSA. But I want to go to Lucknow, because we are from there.

snippet.title: NEW! BREAKING NEWS - Tapu Is Back! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------

snippet.title: The Flash – Official Trailer
snippet.description:
On June 16, worlds collide. Watch the official trailer now for The Flash – only in theaters. #TheFlashMovie 

Warner Bros. Pictures presents “The Flash,” directed by Andy Muschietti (the “IT” films, “Mama”). Ezra Miller reprises their role as Barry Allen in the DC Super Hero’s first-ever standalone feature film.

Worlds collide in “The Flash” when Barry uses his superpowers to travel back in time in order to change the events of the past. But when his attempt to save his family inadvertently alters the future, Barry becomes trapped in a reality in which General Zod has returned, threatening annihilation, and there are no Super Heroes to turn to. That is, unless Barry can coax a very different Batman out of retirement and rescue an imprisoned Kryptonian… albeit not the one he’s looking for. Ultimately, to save the world that he is in and return to the future that he knows, Barry’s only hope is to race for his life. But will making the ultimate sacrifice be enough to reset the universe? 

“The Flash” ensemble also includes rising star Sasha Calle, Michael Shannon (“Bullet Train,” “Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice”), Ron Livingston (“Loudermilk,” “The Conjuring”), Maribel Verdú (“Elite,” “Y tu mamá también”), Kiersey Clemons (“Zack Snyder’s Justice League,” “Sweetheart”), Antje Traue (“King of Ravens,” “Man of Steel”) and Michael Keaton (“Spider-Man: Homecoming,” “Batman”).

“The Flash” is produced by Barbara Muschietti (the “IT” films, “Mama”) and Michael Disco (“Rampage,” “San Andreas”). The screenplay is by Christina Hodson (“Birds of Prey,” “Bumblebee”), with a screen story by John Francis Daley & Jonathan Goldstein (“Dungeons & Dragons: Honor Among Thieves,” “Spider-Man: Homecoming”) and Joby Harold (“Transformers: Rise of the Beasts,” “Army of the Dead”), based on characters from DC. The executive producers 
are Toby Emmerich, Walter Hamada, Galen Vaisman and Marianne Jenkins.

Joining director Muschietti behind the camera are director of photography Henry Braham (“Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3,” “The Suicide Squad”), production designer Paul Denham Austerberry (“IT Chapter Two,” “The Shape of Water”), editors Jason Ballantine (the “IT” films, “The Great Gatsby”) and Paul Machliss (“The Gentlemen,” “Baby Driver”), and costume designer Alexandra Byrne (“Doctor Strange,” “Guardians of the Galaxy”); the score is by Benjamin Wallfisch 
(“The Invisible Man,” the “IT” films).

Warner Bros. Pictures presents a Double Dream/a Disco Factory production of an Andy Muschietti film, “The Flash.” It will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and is set to open in theaters in North America on June 16, 2023 and internationally beginning 14 June 2023.

rooh meri  rehndi

Heeriye

ni tere bina ni

Kde kde message te

Teri photo nal kra

snippet.title: On the 2023 Tripura Legislative Assembly Elections
snippet.description:
Tripura is all set to go to the polls on February 16 to elect all 60 members of the Tripura Legislative Assembly. This time, it’s going to be a triangular fight among the BJP-IPFT alliance, the regional tribal party Tipra Motha, and the Left parties and the Congress combine. 

The tribal issues have taken center stage in the Tripura elections. Pradyot Manikya, the royal scion and leader of Tipra Motha, is pushing for a separate state for the Tripuries, while the left and Congress are advocating for increased power to the tribal autonomous council.

At present over 400 Central Armed Para Military Forces (CAPF) are being deployed in the state along with 20000 police personnel to ensure a peaceful election.

Read Outlook's ground reports and more from the Northeast in its latest issue.

#Tripura #AssemblyElections #Elections2023 #Congress #BJP #CPM #Tribals

गुनगुन गुनगुन गुन गातंय का मन 
सनसन सन सननन करतंय तनमन 

उड उड उडतंय गं उडतंय गं 
बावळं संगं संगं वार्‍याशी सलगी करतंय का मन

सांगना संगं संगं माझ्या तुझंही असंच करतंय का मन
  
सजने, सांगना 
स्वप्नाच्या मागं 
पळ पळ पळताना 

मनाची लय, उराचा ताल पार बदलून जातो
रंगतो असा जिवाचा खेळ... 

गुनगुन गुनगुन गुन गातंय का मन 
सनसन सन सननन करतंय तनमन... 

मोहाच्या फुलानं सजलंय सारं जिनं 
झुलतंय बेहोशीनं काळीज गं खुळं
भेटीच्या ओढीनं मन झालंया दीवानं 
गोंदलं पंखानं आभाळ ह्ये निळं

सांजंला गाभुळत्या  
मन भिरभिर भिर भिरभिरतंय
सतरंगी स्वप्नानं 
कसं रंगतंय ह्ये येडं 

कसली ही माया कसली जादूगरी गं 
काळीज ठेका धरी तालावरी गं 
नुसत्या या सपनानं खरं खरं सांगना तुझं भरतंय का मन... 

सनई घुमली दारी
हां लगीन घटिका आली
खुलली लाली गाली
हां लगीन घटिका आली

उरात झुळुका, जिवात गलका
मनात गं नवलाई 
नव्हाळ हुरहुर, मधाळ काहुर
जोडी जमली 

गुनगुन गुनगुन गुन गातंय का मन...

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3694 - 14 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3694: Toofan Aa Gaya Hai
--------------------------------------------------------
The mysterious person writes a message on Gokuldham's notice board, and Babita notices someone trespassing, so she immediately yells out of fear. Gokuldham's men want to catch the trespasser or the ghost, but they're scared to face him, so Sodhi leads them. All the men go to the garden and try to find the person who might have sent those mysterious gifts. After a long search, they find no traces of any stranger. While all of them gather at Gokuldham Park, suddenly they hear "Sakharam's" horn beep. So, is this anonymous person up to stealing Bhide's "Sakharam"? Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3694, 14 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000209389

snippet.title: Speedrunning Minecraft Twice At The SAME TIME....
snippet.description:
Speedrunning Minecraft Twice At The SAME TIME.... This was INSANE! We couldn't even move without stressing about what might go badly in our other world.

Download Cashapp: https://cash.app

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dream

George:  @GeorgeNotFound 
Sapnap:  @Sapnap 

This is a custom coded 1.19 survival challenge. My friends and I try and beat the game TWICE AT ONCE. We coded a mod that makes it so everything we do on one Minecraft world, happens on another Minecraft world at the same time. We aren't switching between them, we have to control both at the same time!

Can we beat the enderdragon?

Want to see this again? Like the video and we might make this type of video a series!
